Compare Fits with Other Countries to Choose a Plot¶

When Italy had the some number of data points as Turkey today, the red line shows the fitted values and blue dots show the real actualized value.

When China had the some number of data points as Turkey today, the red line shows the fitted values and blue dots show the real actualized value.

When the USA had the some number of data points as Turkey today, the red line shows the fitted values and blue dots show the real actualized value.

When Germany had the some number of data points as Turkey today, the red line shows the fitted values and blue dots show the real actualized value.

As a result, cubic fit seems to be the best for the countries that do not show any sign of flatter curve.¶
